SubjectInterim Order No. 11 Respecting Private Operators
PrecisOrder approving INTERIM ORDER NO. 11 RESPECTING PRIVATE OPERATORS, made by the Minister of Transport on May 31, 2013, in order to provide certification and oversight of private operators while a new regulatory framework is developed as part of the Canadian Aviation Regulations.
